### END OF WORKFLOW
### ===========================================
### 
### Summary of Operations:
### 1. ✓ Parent authentication
### 2. ✓ Child profile creation
### 3. ✓ Upload 5 IEP documents
### 4. ✓ AI extraction with SSE streaming
### 5. ✓ Manual correction workflow
### 6. ✓ Document finalization (JSONB → normalized tables)
### 7. ✓ Progress entry logging
### 8. ✓ Service delivery tracking
### 9. ✓ Dashboard analytics
### 10. ✓ Document download
###
### Red Flags Demonstrated:
### - Document 5 shows vague goals, missing data, service reductions
### - AI should detect and create Smart Prompts
### - Parent can review compliance health and goal mastery metrics
###
